@invobj
(Burns exits the Janson Jungle Cruise, and
enters Adventureville. Shrieks echo from
the prefabricated monster arena, a roller
coaster creaks alarmingly, the taped
cries of kookaburas and hyenas make an
earsplitting din, and, through all this
noise, the sound of chittering is audible
from Bugtown. Burns struggles to focus as
she reads her map.)

Burns: Let's see... Trippyville is to the
east, behind those gates. I'm locked out.
/i
(The park intercom crackles to life.)

Voice: Hello? Agent D. E. Machina here. I
lost my keys to the Trippyville gates. I
think I left them on the bottom floor of
the Dungeon Crawl. Could somebody please
pick them up for me?
